    fr.sorbonne_u.components.ComponentI

    public class HeaterTester
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractComponent
    The class HeaterTester implements a component performing tests for the class Heater as a BCM component.

    Description

    Glass-box Invariants

     invariant       heaterUserInboundPortURI != null && !heaterUserInboundPortURI.isEmpty()
 invariant       heaterInternalControlInboundPortURI != null && !heaterInternalControlInboundPortURI.isEmpty()
 invariant       heaterExternalControlInboundPortURI != null && !heaterExternalControlInboundPortURI.isEmpty()

    Black-box Invariants

     invariant       X_RELATIVE_POSITION >= 0
 invariant       Y_RELATIVE_POSITION >= 0

    Created on : 2021-09-13

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
